&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Hilti Fieldwire, Inc.&#39;s affiliate is hiring. This position is an opportunity to join the Hilti, Inc. team. The candidate selected for this position will be a Hilti, Inc. team member. If interested, please complete our application.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are we looking for?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Mid Market Account Executives (MMAE) for Fieldwire are responsible for driving net new revenue working with a wide range of SMB and Mid Market accounts within the construction industry.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Fieldwire is looking for an experienced Mid Market Account Executive who has a balanced mix of construction and SaaS experience. The MMAE works as a Team with sales management and Construction solutions specialist team to manage qualified opportunities through the full sales cycle from prospecting to close-won business.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The MMAE will build a pipeline from an inbound sales motion through an array of prospecting activities including calls, emails, demonstration requests,etc. to create a significant pipeline of qualified opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you’ll be doing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The primary responsibilities for the Mid Market Account Executive are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Achieve monthly, quarterly quota and annual quota&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and maintain pipeline 3x the size of quota&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Create, demo, nurture, and close deals through inbound prospecting&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Master the ability to evangelize the Fieldwire story&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be an expert in the competitive landscape&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;At Fieldwire, we’re looking for our next Account Executive to have the following skills and experiences:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Minimum 2–3 years of SaaS sales experience; experience in a closing role is a plus&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience managing contract values above £20,000 ARR&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Previous experience selling Construction software is a BIG plus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Successful track record of achieving quota&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-driven and highly motivated to achieve success&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with and negotiating with executive level contacts&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to confidently and effectively speak with prospects at multiple levels &amp;amp; building consensus&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Methodical sales methodology and territory management practices&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in sales motion from the ground up through constructive feedback, piloting and iteration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent diagnostic, communication and presentation skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Self-aware&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coachable &amp;amp; confident&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Do what it takes mentality&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive &amp;amp; curious&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Goal &amp;amp; process-oriented&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
